rlSecuritySuiteSynProtectionMode.description: This scalar globally set protection mode on TCP SYN traffic. Disabled - the system doesn't support protection against TCP SYN attack. Report - the system doesn't support protection against TCP SYN attack,but reports about it. Block - the systems supports protection against TCP SYN attack by blocking this traffic on the port.
